## Summary
This documentation explains how to create and use Calculations in Amplitude, which transform events or event properties into user properties for segmentation. It details the three types of calculation properties (Event Count, Aggregation, First/Last Value), how to create them, and how they can be used in personalization campaigns and analytics charts.

